title: Lamine Yamal no tiene techo: El gol que jamás olvidará en la Champions League
text: [Barcelona](/cronologia/-/meta/barcelona) El joven Lamine Yamal marcó este 19 de septiembre su primer gol en la UEFA Champions League, el torneo de clubes más importante de Europa. En el duelo [AS Mónaco vs FC Barcelona](https://www.laprensa.hn/deportes/monaco-vs-barcelona-champions-league-en-vivo-horario-donde-verlo-hansi-flick-DF21539965), el joven zurdo se hizo presente en el marcador en el momento que más lo necesitaba su equipo ya que estaban perdiendo por la mínima diferencia y para colmo jugando con diez por expulsión de Eric García. Se jugaba el minuto 28, balonazo en profundidad de Pedri, Yamal al borde del área dribló a un rival y sacó un zurdazo que se fue a ras de pasto y se incrustó al ángulo. El portero del AS Mónaco se lanzó, pero le fue imposible de poder y lamentó la anotación. Por su parte Yamal fue felicitado por el resto de sus jugadores del FC Barcelona y una vez más demuestra su calidad. Su tanto fue el primero en la era de Flick en la Liga de Campeones de Europa.

text: Previsão do tempo aponta dia ensolarado hoje (13) para Olímpia (SP) Olímpia (SP) deve ter dia ensolarado hoje (13). title: 星球石墨股价连续3天下跌累计跌幅5.03%，南方基金旗下1只基金持16.76万股，浮亏损失24.3万元|基金_新浪财经_新浪网
text:
8月14日， 星球石墨 跌2.63%，截至发稿，报27.40元/股，成交4601.16万元，换手率1.15%，总市值39.39亿元。星球石墨股价已经连续3天下跌，区间累计跌幅5.03%。
资料显示，南通星球石墨股份有限公司位于江苏省如皋市九华镇华兴路8号，成立日期2001年10月24日，上市日期2021年3月24日，公司主营业务涉及石墨设备的研发、生产、销售及维保服务。主营业务收入构成为：石墨设备53.78%，设备配件20.66%，维保服务10.99%，其他8.67%，其他(补充)5.90%。
从基金十大重仓股角度
数据显示，南方基金旗下1只基金重仓星球石墨。南方智弘混合A（020645）二季度持有股数16.76万股，占基金净值比例为2.13%，位居第八大重仓股。根据测算，今日浮亏损失约12.4万元。连续3天下跌期间浮亏损失24.3万元。
南方智弘混合A（020645）成立日期2024年8月2日，最新规模9864.15万。今年以来收益24.8%，同类排名1641/8197；近一年收益41.29%，同类排名2094/7946；成立以来收益41.15%。
南方智弘混合A（020645）基金经理为金岚枫。
截至发稿，金岚枫累计任职时间4年87天，现任基金资产总规模11.36亿元，任职期间最佳基金回报41.15%， 任职期间最差基金回报3.28%。

title: Dense Fog: Dense Fog Alert: Odisha Districts Brace for Extended Period of Low Visibility | Bhubaneswar News - Times of India
text: Bhubaneswar: IMD forecast on Thursday said dense fog would be very likely to continue in several districts during the next two to three days amid a slight rise trend in minimum temperature. The districts likely to witness this include Puri, Khurda, Nayagarh, Ganjam, Gajapati, Cuttack, Jagatsinghpur, among others. The office of Special Relief Commissioner (SRC) in the wake of IMD's warning sent its routine advisory to district collectors to take needful steps for restricted driving in their respective areas during morning hours. \"Police and transport officials of respective districts may take necessary steps for controlled plying of vehicles on highways during dense fog to avoid any road accident,\" reads the advisory from SRC office. H R Biswas, the regional head of IMD centre in the city said, “Prevailing wind pattern and availability of moisture favour for continue of shallow to moderate or dense fog in the state this week.” He said minimum temperature saw a rise by two to three degrees Celsius at several places in the state and there would be no large change in the prevailing trend of mercury level during the next three-four days. Dense fog reducing visibility to 50 meter or less was reported from towns like Rourkela, Cuttack, Phulbani, Nayagarh and Koraput.We also published the following articles recentlyIMD issues red warning for very dense fog todayThe weather department has issued a red alert for very dense fog in Delhi-NCR on Friday. Experts warn against venturing out in vehicles between 4 am and 10 am due to the high risk of car pile-ups and accidents. Overnight winds on Thursday improved visibility, but Friday is expected to have very low visibility due to decreased wind speed.
